name: Team OG Stick shirt (Black/Red)
description:
Have a genuine love for the arcade days?  Love a good arcade stick?  Show your love with this beautiful design from Team OG.  

Shirts are Gildan Cotton T-Shirts. They feature a seamless collar, taped neck and shoulders. They are also double-needle stiched in the sleeve and bottom hems.  These Gildan shirts are lightweight, so you will be able to wear these in those high stress situations and still look and feel like a champ.
